  "name": "Brine Pool Drone",
  "mood": "Submerged",
  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "Brine pools — hypersaline lakes on the ocean floor — create a visible surface and their own micro-ecosystem. Wavetable src1 (harmonic, warm bank) against Sine src2 at -7 semitones for the dense, almost liquid beat frequency. Drift Bus is the centrepiece: driftRate=0.009 and driftDepth=0.88 creates the slow, viscous evolution of a liquid within a liquid. Journey Mode obligatory. proc1=LP (380 Hz, moderate reso) keeps the warmth dense. proc2=LP (950 Hz) as a gentle upper ceiling. Four mods: LFO->WavetablePos (morphs the harmonic character slowly), Env->FilterCutoff (breathes), Velocity->Volume, Aftertouch->FXMix (sinks deeper into reverb). air=0.1 — dense atmosphere.",
